com.siperian.sif.message

Class ResourcePrivilege

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.siperian.sif.message.ResourcePrivilege
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ResourcePrivilege
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Privileges for a requested resource UID.

    Note, isValid() should be called before the various "has" methods to avoid exceptions.

    See Also:
    GetResourcePrivilegesResponse, Serialized Form
